text: Dad phoned me up twice from your house this morning and couldn't get no answer here, he said, I was sat here so I can here the phone go, anyway he went around again later on, tried it, and it was alright then.
Also in dad's last night said sat up watching the gold fish and he said oh I'll, I'll give you, I'll give you a tank and I'll get some fish on Sunday.
So what did she sa- did you say?
Well she didn't think he was serious,<tv on> he was, so were gonna have to phone up tonight and say look, no fish.
